omain etc\n• Well Versed with L2VPN and L3VPN services .\n• Understanding of Management protocols and technologies – Netconf, gRPC, Open Config, Streaming Telemetry, SNMP etc\n• Understanding of Security Features – RPKI, IPSEC, MACSEC etc\n• Understanding of L2/L3 underlays and overlays.\n\nCross-Functional Collaboration\n• Enabling field team with roadmaps updates – Product, Technology.\n• Working with Field teams to understand customer requirements, analyzing them and translating them into ASks.\n• Working with Engg. teams on feasibility, planning, prioritizing and delivering.\n\nKnowledge and Skills:\n• Extensive team skills and ability to cross functionally drive/influence work through others, ability to mentor and lead teams to achieve results for complex, ambiguous projects.\n• Extensive skills in cost efficient solution building, financial performance metric creation and analysis\n• Extensive business acumen and knowledge of root cause analysis and problem detection.\n• Technical understanding and knowledge of the relevant industry and ability to provide product specific technical training to the team.\n\nAdditional Skills:\n\nCross Domain Knowled	{}	https://careers.hpe.com/us/en/job/1200217/Principal-Product-Manager?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic	\N	\N	\N	\N	2026-04-09 20:37:01.399
