h cross-functional teams and managing multiple priorities effectively. This is a remote-first role, requiring a proactive approach, self-discipline, and a strong ability to work independently. A reliable internet connection and a conducive home office environment are necessary. If you are passionate about building successful FMCG brands and driving growth from a remote setting, we encourage you to apply. Our client is a leader in the industry, offering a collaborative and innovative work culture. This role offers the chance to shape the future of our client's product offerings, contributing significantly to their success, without being tied to a specific physical office location near Patna, Bihar, IN .	{}	https://en-in.whatjobs.com/jobs/fmcg-product-manager/patna-bihar?id=231000313&utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic	\N	\N	\N	\N	2026-04-09 20:37:01.415
